    "2023b), and the number of words and characters vary across sentences.",
    "This is a design flaw of the filters rather than a reflection of GPT's capabilities.",
    "The 12 filters in Table3parse each answer independently, hence they only detect antonyms/synonyms within one answer.",
    "If GPT uses a term in one answer and a synonym in another, this similarity would be missed.",
    "Newer versions of our system have created a dictionary as a supplemental filter to remedy this shortcoming."
